{"search_data": "Central Increase in Remuneration for Asha, ANM & Anganwadi Workers \u2013 PM ModiIncrease in Remuneration for Asha & Anganwadi WorkersThe important features and highlights of the decision to increase remuneration of Asha, ANM and Anganwadi Workers are as follows:-Asha workers who gets encouragement amount (Protsahan Rashi) is now doubledAsha workers and helpers would get insurance coverage of around 4 lakhs for free. This 4 lakh insurance cover includes 2 lakh insurance coverage under PM Jeevan Jyoti Bima Yojana and Rs. 2 lakh insurance under PM Suraksha Bima Yojana. Moreover, all the asha workers and their helpers will not have to pay an premium amount for this insurance and central govt. would bear this cost.Insurance Cover Asha Workers HelpersAlso the honorarium for Anganwadi Workers has been significantly increased:-All those Anganwadi workers who used to get Rs. 3000 so far, would now receive Rs. 4500.Similarly, those workers who were getting Rs. 2250 would now get Rs. 3500.Anganwadi Helpers (Sahayika) would now get Rs. Rs. 2250 instead of previous amount of Rs. 1500.Prime Minister also announced that Anganwadi workers and helpers who uses modern techniques such as Common Application Software (ICDS-CAS), would now get additional incentives. These incentives would range from Rs. 250 to Rs. 500 on the basis of performance of Asha, ANM and Anganwadi workers.\u0915\u0947\u0902\u0926\u094d\u0930 \u0938\u0930\u0915\u093e\u0930 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e \u0906\u0902\u0917\u0928\u0935\u093e\u0921\u093c\u0940 \u0915\u093e\u0930\u094d\u092f\u0915\u0930\u094d\u0924\u093e\u0913\u0902 \u0914\u0930 \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u093f\u0915\u093e\u0913\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u093e\u0928\u0926\u0947\u092f \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0905\u092d\u0942\u0924\u092a\u0942\u0930\u094d\u0935 \u092c\u0922\u093c\u094b\u0924\u0930\u0940\u0964 pic.twitter.com/XhRE3CQr9L\u2014 BJP (@BJP4India) September 11, 2018 PM addresses these Asha workers, ANM, and Anganwadi Workers as \u201cApne Lakh Haath\u201d and said that the primary focus of govt. is to ensure quality \u201cHealth for All\u201d. Immunization process of new born babies and giving proper education to mothers is being carried out on a massive scale.PM Modi also lay emphasis on proper vaccination to benefit both mother and children. Now the training process of Asha, ANM and Anganwadi workers is now simplified with the introduction of new technology. PM interacted with teams of three as \u2013 the ASHA worker, Anganwadi worker and ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwife) from across the country through video conferencing.He appreciated their efforts to work together, making usage of innovative technology and to improve the delivery of health and nutrition services and achieve the goal of the POSHAN Abhiyan.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}